    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Bobbin lace with continuous threads decorated with geometric motifs. Inspired by 17th century Genoese bobbin lace, Cluny has become one of the most widely produced hand-made laces.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
